    <section id="id43975379">
      <title>Content</title>
      <para id="id44086085">Activity: To use a range of techniques for performing calculations [LO 1.10.2, LO 1.10.5]</para>
      <para id="id44086093"/>
      <para id="id44086349">1. It helps a lot to first ESTIMATE an answer before you calculate the quotient. Work through the following examples with a friend:</para>
      <para id="id44086164">
        <figure id="id44086169">
          <media id="id44086169_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/jpg" src="../../media/Pencil.jpg" id="id44086169__onlineimage" height="310" width="577"/>
          </media>
        </figure>
      </para>
      <para id="id42699815">2. Complete the following table on your own. You may use a calculator for the answers in the last column.</para>
