    <section id="id44857811">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id44857818"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Outcome 1:</emphasis> The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id44395630"><emphasis effect="bold">Assessment Standard 1.10:</emphasis> We know this when the learner uses a range of techniques to perform written and mental calculations with whole numbers including:</para>
      <para id="id44513796"><emphasis effect="bold">1.10.2:</emphasis> long division;</para>
      <para id="id44513804"><emphasis effect="bold">1.10.5:</emphasis> using a calculator.</para>
